{"image_id": "UNM_2016_page_151", "image_size": [1275, 1669], "ocr": [{"text": "149", "bbox": [1192.0, 1605.6, 1216.7, 1622.3]}, {"text": "Unum 2016 Annual Report", "bbox": [996.1, 1606.0, 1151.0, 1622.3]}, {"text": "The fair value is represented by the actuarial present value of future cash flows of the contracts.", "bbox": [168.8, 241.6, 887.4, 262.5]}, {"text": "Changes in our OPEB plan assets measured at fair value on a recurring basis using significant unobservable inputs (Level 3) during the", "bbox": [168.8, 270.7, 1176.4, 291.7]}, {"text": "years ended December 31, 2016 and 2015 are as follows:", "bbox": [131.2, 299.9, 560.7, 320.9]}, {"text": "Year Ended December 31, 2016", "bbox": [696.4, 341.3, 916.1, 360.0]}, {"text": "Beginning", "bbox": [481.0, 370.5, 552.9, 389.2]}, {"text": "Actual Return", "bbox": [623.8, 370.5, 718.4, 389.2]}, {"text": "Net Benefits and", "bbox": [906.3, 370.5, 1028.1, 389.2]}, {"text": "End", "bbox": [1102.5, 370.5, 1131.3, 389.2]}, {"text": "(in millions of dollars)", "bbox": [131.3, 395.5, 282.6, 414.2]}, {"text": "of Year", "bbox": [490.9, 395.5, 543.0, 414.2]}, {"text": "on Plan Assets", "bbox": [620.0, 395.5, 722.1, 414.2]}, {"text": "Contributions", "bbox": [766.7, 395.5, 858.8, 414.2]}, {"text": "Expenses Paid", "bbox": [915.1, 395.5, 1014.5, 414.2]}, {"text": "of Year", "bbox": [1090.9, 395.5, 1138.3, 414.2]}, {"text": "Life Insurance Contracts", "bbox": [131.2, 427.0, 314.3, 448.0]}, {"text": "$11.2", "bbox": [491.1, 426.9, 540.6, 448.0]}, {"text": "$0.1", "bbox": [651.0, 426.9, 690.6, 448.0]}, {"text": "$15.1", "bbox": [791.1, 426.9, 840.6, 448.0]}, {"text": "$(15.6)", "bbox": [934.3, 426.9, 997.4, 448.0]}, {"text": "$10.8", "bbox": [1091.1, 426.9, 1135.4, 448.0]}, {"text": "Year Ended December 31, 2015", "bbox": [699.7, 489.3, 912.8, 507.9]}, {"text": "Beginning", "bbox": [481.0, 518.5, 552.9, 537.1]}, {"text": "Actual Return", "bbox": [623.8, 518.5, 718.4, 537.1]}, {"text": "Net Benefits and", "bbox": [906.3, 518.5, 1028.1, 537.1]}, {"text": "End", "bbox": [1102.5, 518.5, 1131.3, 537.1]}, {"text": "(in millions of dollars)", "bbox": [131.3, 543.5, 282.6, 562.1]}, {"text": "of Year", "bbox": [490.9, 543.5, 543.0, 562.1]}, {"text": "on Plan Assets", "bbox": [620.0, 543.5, 722.1, 562.1]}, {"text": "Contributions", "bbox": [766.7, 543.5, 858.8, 562.1]}, {"text": "Expenses Paid", "bbox": [915.1, 543.5, 1014.5, 562.1]}, {"text": "of Year", "bbox": [1090.9, 543.5, 1138.3, 562.1]}, {"text": "Life Insurance Contracts", "bbox": [131.2, 574.9, 314.3, 595.9]}, {"text": "$11.3", "bbox": [492.8, 574.9, 540.7, 595.9]}, {"text": "$0.3", "bbox": [652.3, 574.9, 690.7, 595.9]}, {"text": "$15.8", "bbox": [792.8, 574.9, 840.7, 595.9]}, {"text": "$(16.2)", "bbox": [936.3, 574.9, 997.1, 595.9]}, {"text": "$11.2", "bbox": [1092.8, 574.9, 1135.4, 595.9]}, {"text": "For the years ended December 31, 2016 and 2015, the actual return on plan assets relates solely to investments still held at the reporting", "bbox": [168.8, 627.0, 1184.8, 648.0]}, {"text": "date. There were no transfers into or out of Level 3 during 2016 or 2015.", "bbox": [131.2, 656.2, 660.7, 677.2]}, {"text": "Measurement Assumptions", "bbox": [131.2, 705.2, 445.7, 737.9]}, {"text": "We use a December 31 measurement date for each of our plans. The weighted average assumptions used in the measurement of our", "bbox": [168.8, 743.7, 1176.7, 764.7]}, {"text": "benefit obligations as of December 31 and our net periodic benefit costs for the years ended December 31 are as follows:", "bbox": [131.2, 772.9, 1041.5, 793.9]}, {"text": "Pension Benefits", "bbox": [644.4, 814.3, 755.6, 833.0]}, {"text": "U.S. Plans", "bbox": [555.2, 839.3, 624.5, 858.0]}, {"text": "U.K. Plan", "bbox": [789.5, 839.3, 852.7, 858.0]}, {"text": "OPEB", "bbox": [1039.0, 839.3, 1073.5, 858.0]}, {"text": "2016", "bbox": [514.8, 864.3, 554.7, 883.0]}, {"text": "2015", "bbox": [634.7, 864.3, 673.4, 883.0]}, {"text": "2016", "bbox": [752.3, 864.3, 792.2, 883.0]}, {"text": "2015", "bbox": [872.2, 864.3, 910.9, 883.0]}, {"text": "2016", "bbox": [989.8, 864.3, 1029.7, 883.0]}, {"text": "2015", "bbox": [1109.7, 864.3, 1143.8, 883.0]}, {"text": "Benefit Obligations", "bbox": [131.2, 894.6, 291.1, 915.8]}, {"text": "Discount Rate", "bbox": [156.2, 923.9, 264.6, 944.9]}, {"text": "4.40%", "bbox": [515.6, 923.9, 571.3, 945.0]}, {"text": "4.80%", "bbox": [635.7, 923.9, 689.7, 944.9]}, {"text": "2.70%", "bbox": [753.1, 923.9, 808.8, 945.0]}, {"text": "3.80%", "bbox": [873.2, 923.9, 927.2, 944.9]}, {"text": "4.20%", "bbox": [990.6, 923.9, 1046.3, 945.0]}, {"text": "4.70%", "bbox": [1110.7, 923.9, 1159.4, 944.9]}, {"text": "Rate of Compensation Increase", "bbox": [156.2, 953.1, 395.7, 974.1]}, {"text": "N/A", "bbox": [516.3, 953.0, 555.2, 974.1]}, {"text": "N/A", "bbox": [635.6, 953.1, 674.0, 974.1]}, {"text": "3.80%", "bbox": [753.1, 953.0, 808.8, 974.1]}, {"text": "3.60%", "bbox": [873.2, 953.1, 927.2, 974.1]}, {"text": "N/A", "bbox": [991.3, 953.0, 1030.2, 974.1]}, {"text": "N/A", "bbox": [1110.6, 953.1, 1143.7, 974.1]}, {"text": "Net Periodic Benefit Cost", "bbox": [131.2, 989.4, 336.8, 1010.6]}, {"text": "Discount Rate", "bbox": [156.2, 1018.8, 264.6, 1039.7]}, {"text": "4.80%", "bbox": [515.6, 1018.7, 571.3, 1039.8]}, {"text": "4.40%", "bbox": [635.7, 1018.8, 689.7, 1039.7]}, {"text": "3.80%", "bbox": [753.1, 1018.7, 808.8, 1039.8]}, {"text": "3.60%", "bbox": [873.2, 1018.8, 927.2, 1039.7]}, {"text": "4.70%", "bbox": [990.6, 1018.7, 1046.3, 1039.8]}, {"text": "4.30%", "bbox": [1110.7, 1018.8, 1159.4, 1039.7]}, {"text": "Expected Return on Plan Assets", "bbox": [156.2, 1047.9, 398.8, 1068.9]}, {"text": "7.50%", "bbox": [515.6, 1047.8, 571.3, 1068.9]}, {"text": "7.50%", "bbox": [635.7, 1047.9, 689.7, 1068.9]}, {"text": "4.90%", "bbox": [753.1, 1047.8, 808.8, 1068.9]}, {"text": "5.20%", "bbox": [873.2, 1047.9, 927.2, 1068.9]}, {"text": "5.75%", "bbox": [990.6, 1047.8, 1046.3, 1068.9]}, {"text": "5.75%", "bbox": [1110.7, 1047.9, 1159.4, 1068.9]}, {"text": "Rate of Compensation Increase", "bbox": [156.2, 1077.1, 395.7, 1098.1]}, {"text": "N/A", "bbox": [516.3, 1077.0, 555.2, 1098.1]}, {"text": "N/A", "bbox": [635.6, 1077.1, 674.0, 1098.1]}, {"text": "3.60%", "bbox": [753.1, 1077.0, 808.8, 1098.1]}, {"text": "3.60%", "bbox": [873.2, 1077.1, 927.2, 1098.1]}, {"text": "N/A", "bbox": [991.3, 1077.0, 1030.2, 1098.1]}, {"text": "N/A", "bbox": [1110.6, 1077.1, 1143.7, 1098.1]}, {"text": "We set the discount rate assumption annually for each of our retirement-related benefit plans at the measurement date to reflect", "bbox": [168.8, 1135.4, 1144.8, 1156.4]}, {"text": "the yield on a portfolio of high quality fixed income corporate debt instruments matched against the projected cash flows for future benefits.", "bbox": [131.2, 1164.6, 1179.9, 1185.6]}, {"text": "Our long-term rate of return on plan assets assumption is selected from a range of probable return outcomes generated by statistical", "bbox": [168.8, 1193.8, 1169.9, 1214.8]}, {"text": "analysis of the asset portfolio. Our expectations for the future investment returns of the asset categories are based on a combination of", "bbox": [131.2, 1223.0, 1151.3, 1244.0]}, {"text": "historical market performance, evaluations of investment forecasts obtained from external consultants and economists, and current market", "bbox": [131.2, 1252.2, 1182.5, 1273.1]}, {"text": "yields. The methodology underlying the return assumption includes the various elements of the expected return for each asset class such", "bbox": [131.2, 1281.3, 1168.4, 1302.3]}, {"text": "as long-term rates of return, volatility of returns, and the correlation of returns between various asset classes. The expected return for the", "bbox": [131.2, 1310.5, 1174.4, 1331.5]}, {"text": "total portfolio is calculated based on the plan’s strategic asset allocation. Investment risk is measured and monitored on an ongoing basis", "bbox": [131.2, 1339.7, 1165.4, 1360.7]}, {"text": "through annual liability measurements, periodic asset/liability studies, and quarterly investment portfolio reviews. Risk tolerance is", "bbox": [131.2, 1368.9, 1122.9, 1389.9]}, {"text": "established through consideration of plan liabilities, plan funded status, and corporate financial condition.", "bbox": [131.2, 1398.1, 920.0, 1419.0]}]}